#!/bin/sh
"Lines that start with quotation marks are comments."
"The first line tricks the editor into using shell script syntax highlighting."

"This file simply loads the modeless presets for vim."

"If you place this file inside ~/.vim, vim should automatically detect it."
"If it fails to do so, you can create a symbolic link from ~/.vimrc to this file."
"See README.md for details."

runtime modeless.vimrc
